who are we?

We build boutique designed homes with passion for building and the quality of our finished product to last for life. The day we started building our focus is on making your experience hassle free, rewarding and enjoyable. We understand how daunting your building experience can be especially if you are building for first time. That is why we offer flexibility, cooperation and friendly service so that your needs are met in a way that suits you the best…
